{"title":"风雨夕","authors":["陈挺苏"],"dates":[{"year":1982,"month":8,"day":2}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"风雨夕"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"陈挺苏"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"望眼乡关隔暮烟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"奈何难见月团圆。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"依稀形影犹如昨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"聚散神伤不两全。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"花谢花开总自怜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都因风雨寸心悬。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"孤怀洒尽伤时泪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"惆怅栖迟三十年。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"原载《自立晚报》"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":3,"page_end":3}